name: Christmas cutie
description:
A cute little wombat making a heck of a mess "helping" with wrapping up the presents and loving every minute. This was inspired by my little wombat/daughter who loves wrapping and adds flowers and stickytape to everything with a cheeky grin. 
[Note - My daughter decided that the Holly was needed herself and asked to be able to draw it in. I think you will agree she was spot on, so this painting is from both of us with love.]

Wishing you a very Merry Christmas or Happy Holiday and all the best for the year to come.

Size - approximately 11cm square png, 300ppi
